    <item>
      <title>随着零售商寻求接触中国消费者的新方式，“代购”走向企业化</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/daigou-goes-corporate-retailers-seek-new-ways-reach-chinese-shoppers-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代购翻译为“代表购买”。在大流行之前，数百万中国人通过购买海外更便宜的商品然后在国内转售来谋生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/daigou-goes-corporate-retailers-seek-new-ways-reach-chinese-shoppers-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 01:23:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国地震灾民在零下严寒中被安全救出</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-rescuers-brave-freezing-cold-find-earthquake-survivors-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，救援人员冒着零度以下的寒冷，将中国西北部甘肃省偏远地区地震的受害者救出，而幸存者将面临未来几个月的不确定性，没有永久的住所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-rescuers-brave-freezing-cold-find-earthquake-survivors-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 03:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
